*Srećan* je bio što je završio fakultet. (He was happy that he finished college.)

Kada je videla njegov *srećan* izraz lica, njoj je postalo jasno da je uspeo. (When she saw his happy expression, it became clear to her that he had succeeded.)

Njegova *srećna* žena je videla da je uspeo. (His happy wife saw that he had succeeded.)

*Srećan* je što je bio u mogućnosti da ispuni njegove želje. (He was happy to be able to fulfill his wishes.)

Kada je čuo veselu vest, bio je *srećan*. (When he heard the good news, he was happy.)